trans-unit.source: Represents the behavior of a dependency property.

Attributes applicable to the dependency property, such as <xref href="System.ComponentModel.DesignerSerializationVisibilityAttribute"></xref> and <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Compiler.ValidationOptionAttribute"></xref>.
Gets or sets the default value of the associated dependency property.
This property can be a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
An object representing the default value for this <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref>.
Attempting to set this property when <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.IsSealed"></xref> is `true.`
Retrieves an array that contains all attributes.
An array that contains all attributes.
Receives an array of type that contains those attributes having type equal to attributeType.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> of attributes to return.
An array of type that contains those attributes having type equal to attributeType.

Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.GetValueOverride"></xref> callback, a callback invoked immediately upon a call to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)"></xref> method.

The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.GetValueOverride"></xref> callback, a callback invoked immediately upon a call to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.GetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty)"></xref> method.
Attempting to set this property when <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.IsSealed"></xref> is `true.`

Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.Options"></xref> is set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.Metadata"></xref>.
`true` if this option is set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.Metadata"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.

Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.Options"></xref> is set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.NonSerialized"></xref>.
`true` if set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.NonSerialized"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.

Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.Options"></xref> are set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.ReadOnly"></xref>.
`true` if set to <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyPropertyOptions.ReadOnly"></xref>; otherwise, `false`.
Gets a value that indicates whether the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref> has been applied to a property resulting in the immutable state.
When the PropertyMetadata.IsSealed is equal to `true`, the following operations cause a <xref:System.InvalidOperationException> to be raised:
Attempting to set the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.DefaultValue%2A>.
Attempting to set the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.Options%2A>.
Attempting to set the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A>.
Attempting to set the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.GetValueOverride%2A>.
`true` if the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref> is immutable; otherwise, `false`.
Provides processing when this <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref> is applied to a dependency property.
Sends notification that this metadata has been applied to a property, and the metadata is being sealed.
This routine is no-op in this implementation.
The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty"></xref> to which this <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref> has been applied.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> associated with this metadata if this instance is type-specific metadata.
If this is default metadata, this value is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).

Gets or set the property which represents the option setting for the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty"></xref> associated to this <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref>.
The possible values for this property are:
The option setting for the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty"></xref> associated to this <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata"></xref>.
Attempting to set this property when <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.IsSealed"></xref> is `true.`

Gets or sets the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.SetValueOverride"></xref> callback, a callback invoked immediately upon a call to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty,System.Object)"></xref> method.

The <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.SetValueOverride"></xref> callback, a callback invoked immediately upon a call to the <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue(System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty,System.Object)"></xref> method.
Trying to set this property when <xref href="System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.IsSealed"></xref> is `true.`
